---
import Layout from "../../layouts/Layout.astro";
---

<Layout
  title="Medication Management in Idaho | MWRS"
  description="Psychiatric evaluation and medication management for adults and teens in Coeur d’Alene and Ponderay, with telehealth available across Idaho and Washington."
>
  <main class="subpage">
    <!-- Hero -->
    <section class="subpage-hero">
      <div class="subpage-hero-inner">
        <h1>Medication Management</h1>
        <p>
          MWRS provides psychiatric medication management for adults and teens.
          Our nurse practitioners focus on careful evaluation, clear
          explanations, and ongoing follow-up so medication is one thoughtful
          part of your care—never the whole story.
        </p>
        <a href="/contact-us" class="subpage-btn"> Start medication care </a>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Light SEO body -->
    <section class="subpage-section">
      <div class="subpage-inner">
        <h2>Who medication care may help</h2>
        <p>
          Medication isn’t the right fit for everyone, but it can be a helpful
          tool at certain points in life. People often seek medication support
          when experiencing:
        </p>

        <ul>
          <li>Ongoing anxiety or panic symptoms</li>
          <li>Depressive symptoms that feel hard to shake</li>
          <li>Sleep disruption related to mood or stress</li>
          <li>Attention, focus, or impulse-control concerns</li>
          <li>Mood shifts that make daily life feel unstable</li>
        </ul>

        <p>
          You don’t have to know in advance whether you “want meds.” Your
          provider can help you think through options, including when counseling
          alone may be the better first step.
        </p>

        <h3>What to expect from visits</h3>
        <p>
          Your first appointment is an evaluation. Your nurse practitioner will
          ask about your symptoms, history, current medications or supplements,
          and what has or hasn’t helped in the past.
        </p>
        <p>
          Together you’ll talk through possible options, which may include
          starting or adjusting a psychiatric medication, coordinating with your
          counselor, ordering lab work when clinically appropriate, and building
          non-medication strategies that support your goals.
        </p>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Bottom CTA -->
    <section class="subpage-section subpage-cta">
      <div class="subpage-inner">
        <h2>Ready to talk about medication?</h2>
        <p>
          Share a bit about what you’re experiencing, and our team will help you
          determine whether a medication consultation makes sense for your
          situation.
        </p>
        <a href="/contact-us" class="subpage-btn"> Start medication care </a>
      </div>
    </section>
  </main>

  <style>
    .subpage {
      background: #f9fafb;
      min-height: 100vh;
    }

    /* Hero */
    .subpage-hero {
      padding: 10rem 1.5rem 3rem;
      background: #fbfbf9;
      border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(15, 23, 42, 0.08);
    }

    .subpage-hero-inner {
      max-width: 900px;
      margin: 0 auto;
      text-align: center;
    }

    .subpage-hero h1 {
      font-family: "Belleza", sans-serif;
      font-size: clamp(2rem, 3vw, 2.6rem);
      letter-spacing: 0.16em;
      text-transform: uppercase;
      margin: 0 0 1rem;
      color: #111827;
    }

    .subpage-hero p {
      margin: 0 0 1.6rem;
      font-size: 1rem;
      line-height: 1.8;
      color: #4b5563;
    }

    /* Outline button (same top & bottom) */
    .subpage-btn {
      display: inline-block;
      padding: 0.85rem 1.9rem;
      border-radius: 999px;
      border: 1px solid #0f172a;
      font-size: 0.9rem;
      text-transform: uppercase;
      letter-spacing: 0.14em;
      text-decoration: none;
      background: #ffffff;
      color: #0f172a;
      box-shadow: 0 6px 16px rgba(15, 23, 42, 0.12);
      transition:
        background 0.15s ease,
        color 0.15s ease,
        box-shadow 0.15s ease,
        transform 0.15s ease;
    }

    .subpage-btn:hover {
      background: #0f172a;
      color: #ffffff;
      transform: translateY(-1px);
      box-shadow: 0 10px 24px rgba(15, 23, 42, 0.2);
    }

    /* Body sections */
    .subpage-section {
      padding: 3rem 1.5rem 3.2rem;
      background: #e5e9f3;
      border-top: 1px solid rgba(15, 23, 42, 0.03);
    }

    .subpage-cta {
      background: #fbfbf9;
      text-align: center;
      border-top: 1px solid rgba(15, 23, 42, 0.06);
    }

    .subpage-inner {
      max-width: 900px;
      margin: 0 auto;
    }

    .subpage-section h2 {
      font-family: "Belleza", sans-serif;
      font-size: 1.2rem;
      letter-spacing: 0.18em;
      text-transform: uppercase;
      margin: 0 0 1rem;
      color: #111827;
    }

    .subpage-section h3 {
      margin: 1.1rem 0 0.6rem;
      font-size: 0.98rem;
      font-weight: 500;
      color: #111827;
    }

    .subpage-section p {
      margin: 0 0 0.9rem;
      font-size: 0.96rem;
      line-height: 1.8;
      color: #4b5563;
    }

    .subpage-section ul {
      margin: 0 0 1rem;
      padding-left: 1.1rem;
      font-size: 0.95rem;
      line-height: 1.6;
      color: #4b5563;
    }

    .subpage-section li + li {
      margin-top: 0.2rem;
    }

    .subpage-cta p {
      max-width: 620px;
      margin-left: auto;
      margin-right: auto;
    }
  </style>
</Layout>
